<p>Peaky Blinders begins in 1919, after the First World War that left damaged men and a fractured society. </p>

<p>Three of the Shelby brothers, Arthur, John (played by Joe Cole) and Thomas, served in France during the conflict, and this classic cocktail inspired by the era uses French vermouth.</p>

<p>For 1 glass – Preparation: 5 minutes</p>

<p>Pour the whiskey, the vermouth, the crème de menthe and the Chartreuse into a shaker filled with ice. </p>

<p>Shake well and pour through a strainer into a Champagne coupe or saucer, or a cocktail glass.</p>

